data.description: Welcome to 1055 Lake Village Drive, where your dream home awaits. This stunning property offers a perfect blend of comfort and style with its 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. As you step inside, you'll be captivated by the open floor plan that effortlessly connects the living and dining areas. It's an ideal space for entertaining, allowing you to host gatherings with ease. The living room boasts a cozy fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere that's perfect for those chilly evenings. The master suite is a true retreat. With a generously sized bedroom, a spacious bathroom, and a walk-in closet, it's a space designed for your relaxation and convenience. Say goodbye to clutter and hello to a peaceful oasis. Upstairs, you'll discover a versatile loft area. Whether you need a home office, a playroom, or a cozy reading nook, this space can be customized to suit your unique needs. It's an excellent addition that enhances the functionality of the home. Outside, this community has something for everyone. From the inviting pool for those sunny days to the playground for the little ones, it's a place where you can relax, socialize, and enjoy the outdoors without ever leaving your neighborhood. Don't miss the chance to make it your own and start creating beautiful memories. Your dream home is now a reality at 1055 Lake Village Drive.
